---
title: BeaconLink Agent Heartbeat Sequence
---

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Agent as BeaconLink Agent
    participant Runtime as Runtime Manager
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter
    participant Relay as Relay Network
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant Control as BeaconLink Control Plane
    participant Policy as Policy Engine
    participant Inventory as Inventory Service
    participant Scheduler as Distributed Scheduler
    participant Events as Event Streaming Platform
    participant Audit as Audit Service

    %% =====================================================
    %% Heartbeat Preparation
    %% =====================================================

    Note over Agent: Continuous reconciliation loop triggers heartbeat

    Agent->>Runtime: Collect runtime status
    Runtime->>Adapter: Query runtime health
    Adapter-->>Runtime: Runtime metrics

    Runtime-->>Agent: Runtime summary

    Agent->>Agent: Collect local metrics
    Agent->>Agent: Collect reconciliation status
    Agent->>Agent: Collect deployment status

    %% =====================================================
    %% Secure Transmission
    %% =====================================================

    Agent->>Relay: Send heartbeat (mTLS)

    Note right of Agent: Includes:\n• Agent ID\n• Current Revision\n• Runtime Health\n• Resource Usage\n• Active Deployments\n• Reconciliation Status\n• Timestamp

    Relay->>Gateway: Forward heartbeat
    Gateway->>Control: Deliver heartbeat

    %% =====================================================
    %% Identity Validation
    %% =====================================================

    Control->>Policy: Validate active identity
    Policy-->>Control: Identity trusted

    %% =====================================================
    %% State Update
    %% =====================================================

    Control->>Inventory: Update agent health
    Control->>Inventory: Update runtime metrics
    Control->>Inventory: Update capacity
    Inventory-->>Control: Inventory updated

    %% =====================================================
    %% Scheduler Synchronization
    %% =====================================================

    Control->>Scheduler: Refresh execution capacity
    Scheduler-->>Control: Scheduling state updated

    %% =====================================================
    %% Drift Detection
    %% =====================================================

    Control->>Control: Compare desired vs actual state

    alt Drift Detected

        Control->>Events: Publish DriftDetected
        Control->>Agent: Reconciliation required

    else No Drift

        Note over Control: Desired state satisfied

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Desired State Check
    %% =====================================================

    Control->>Control: Check for new revisions

    alt New Desired State Available

        Control->>Agent: Deliver updated desired state
        Agent->>Agent: Persist revision
        Agent->>Agent: Begin reconciliation

    else No Updates

        Control-->>Agent: Heartbeat acknowledged

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Health Monitoring
    %% =====================================================

    Control->>Control: Evaluate health thresholds

    alt Agent Unhealthy

        Control->>Events: Publish AgentUnhealthy
        Control->>Audit: Record health degradation

    else Agent Healthy

        Control->>Audit: Record successful heartbeat

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Continuous Loop
    %% =====================================================

    loop Every Heartbeat Interval

        Agent->>Runtime: Refresh runtime status
        Runtime-->>Agent: Updated metrics

        Agent->>Relay: Next heartbeat
        Relay->>Control: Forward heartbeat

        Control->>Policy: Continuous authorization
        Policy-->>Control: Authorized

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Timeout Handling
    %% =====================================================

    alt Heartbeat Timeout

        Control->>Events: Publish AgentOffline
        Control->>Scheduler: Remove execution capacity
        Control->>Audit: Record heartbeat timeout

    else Heartbeats Continue

        Note over Agent,Control: Agent remains healthy,<br/>trusted, and continuously synchronized.

    end